print('平均单笔超额收益率：{0:.2f}%'.format(float(total_trades_hold['excess'].mean() * 100)))

total_trades_hold_pos = total_trades_hold[total_trades_hold['return']>0]
total_trades_hold_neg = total_trades_hold[total_trades_hold['return']<0]
print('正收益比率：{0:.2f}%'.format(total_trades_hold_pos.shape[0] / total_trades_hold.shape[0] * 100))
print('平均单笔正收益率：{0:.2f}%'.format(total_trades_hold_pos['return'].mean() * 100))
print('平均单笔负收益率：{0:.2f}%'.format(total_trades_hold_neg['return'].mean() * 100))
